info: Roblox Corporation develops and operates an online entertainment platform. It offers Roblox Studio, a tool that allows users to learn coding, computer science principles, animation, 3D design, and development; and Roblox Education for learning experiences. It serves customers in the United States, Canada, Europe, the Asia-Pacific, and internationally. Roblox Corporation was incorporated in 2004 and is based in San Mateo, California.
